snippet.title: On a Journey RPG (Game Trailer)
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam🙌: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2639150/On_A_Journey_RPG/ 🌟
Join on Discord 🔁:  https://discord.com/invite/hU89aFNVu3  
Follow on X 👀: https://x.com/OnAJourneyRPG
& Subscribe to support the Channel! 

On a Journey - Coming to Steam!

Demo release - September 24th - 2024

A Golden-Age of 2D JRPG's returns with Turn-Based Combat & Retro-Inspired Graphics! Adventure across the world, meet new friends and unlock powerful Summon Monsters as you battle against a truly formidable enemy in this Story-Rich JRPG. Made with RPG Maker MZ. Available to wishlist on Steam.
